 * Copyright (c) 2008-2014 Pierre Cassat
 * <http://github.com/piwi/markdown-extended>
 *
 * Based on MultiMarkdown
 * Copyright (c) 2005-2009 Fletcher T. Penney
 * <http://fletcherpenney.net/>
